{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01HoZSWU78kxApUKeWjxqEKR","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01NRwHMFDdo6UBCsfWfMgEqN","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspaces/rng-utopia/docs/specs/101-lord-of-the-rngs/spec.md","old_string":"- [ ] [frontend] Update `LordOfRngsContext.tsx` — replace mock-simulation imports with chain.ts calls. Wire `joinTierRound` → `buildJoinRoundTx` + `sendAndConfirm`. Wire `buyMoreEntriesAction` → `buildBuyMoreEntriesTx` + `sendAndConfirm`. Wire `claimPayout` → `buildClaimPayoutTx` + `sendAndConfirm` (auto-triggered on win). Add `startSpin` action → `buildStartSpinTx` + `sendAndConfirm` (triggered by \"Spin\" button). Poll/subscribe round account so all clients detect phase transition to Locked as soon as anyone spins (disable Spin button, start animation). Verify: TypeScript compiles, `pnpm lint` clean.","new_string":"- [x] [frontend] Update `LordOfRngsContext.tsx` — replace mock-simulation imports with chain.ts calls. Wire `joinTierRound` → `buildJoinRoundTx` + `sendAndConfirm`. Wire `buyMoreEntriesAction` → `buildBuyMoreEntriesTx` + `sendAndConfirm`. Wire `claimPayout` → `buildClaimPayoutTx` + `sendAndConfirm` (auto-triggered on win). Add `startSpin` action → `buildStartSpinTx` + `sendAndConfirm` (triggered by \"Spin\" button). Poll/subscribe round account so all clients detect phase transition to Locked as soon as anyone spins (disable Spin button, start animation). Verify: TypeScript compiles, `pnpm lint` clean. (done: iteration 15)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":251,"cache_read_input_tokens":118310,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":251},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"cc54e4bc-17c9-4774-b61a